items.title: Thousands protest in Georgia as new president sworn in
items.description: Former head of state Zourabichvili agreed to leave the presidential residence but vowed to fight on.

items.title: Video captures moments before South Korea plane crash
items.description: The Jeju Air flight landing at Muan Airport had 181 passengers on board when it crashed off the runway.

items.title: As Putin reaches 25 years in power, has he 'taken care of Russia'?
items.description: Over a quarter of a century in power we've seen many different Putins, says the BBC's Russia editor.

items.title: Putin apologises over Azerbaijan plane crash, without saying Russia at fault
items.description: Russia's leader apologises over the downing of an Azerbaijani plane in Russian airspace - without directly taking blame.

items.title: Toddler nearly runs off cliff at Hawaii volcano
items.description: The little boy wandered off from his family and "ran straight toward the 400ft cliff edge" of the Kilauea volcano.
